item.description:
This Python script retrieves computer&rsquo;s external IP address (using internet.yandex.ru) and emails message with new IP if IP has been changed since last check. BeautifulSoup module is needed, so install it if you have no installed version:
sudo pip install beautifulsoup Script:
#!/usr/bin/env python  from BeautifulSoup import BeautifulSoup import urllib2 import re import smtplib from email.mime.text import MIMEText  logFile = &#39;/var/log/ippywatchdog.log&#39;  request = urllib2.urlopen(&#39;http://internet.yandex.ru&#39;)  soup = BeautifulSoup(request) yandexIpResponse = soup.
